OL,3,CPlans to pave Broad Street criticised
OL,4,Cover accessibility issues
OL,6,FSome also worry that paving the area
OL,7,Fwill see the loss of Broad Street's
OL,8,Fcurrent disabled parking bays.
OL,10,FJersey's Infrastructure Minister,
OL,11,FConstable Andy Jehan, says the
OL,12,FGovernment are talking to Liberty Bus
OL,13,Fto work on a solution but adds that St
OL,14,FHelier's hopper bus would make it easy
OL,15,Ffor passengers to access the town.
OL,17,FMore spaces for blue badge holders
OL,18,Fwill also be created nearby.
