OL,3,CPlans to pave Broad Street criticised
OL,4,Cover accessibility issues
OL,6,FMr Jehan explains: "Part of our
OL,7,Fpriorities is to make St Helier a more
OL,8,Fvibrant place so we're looking to
OL,9,Fimprove the public morale.
OL,11,F"We need to go ahead and make Broad
OL,12,FStreet a community space where people
OL,13,Fcan relax, sit down and enjoy the
OL,14,Farea."
OL,16,FBroad Street has been closed to most
OL,17,Ftraffic since May 2020 when it was
OL,18,Fbrought in to support social
OL,19,Fdistancing in the early stages of the
OL,20,FCovid pandemic.
